fees.description:
Move-In/Move Out Meter Read fee
For information on additional fees, a full schedule of charges is available from www.momentumenergy.com.au/fees
A 0.53% fee (GST Incl) will apply to payments made by any credit or debit card.

gasContract.terms: Full terms and conditions can be obtained from www.momentumenergy.com.au/terms or by contacting our Customer Care Team on 1800 SWITCH.
gasContract.variation: We will give you written notice of any variations to your rates & charges under your terms and conditions in accordance with applicable legal requirements.

incentives.eligibility: A one-off $50 (GST incl) sign-up credit will be applied to your first gas bill. This credit cannot be redeemed for cash or transferred to another supply address.

eligibility.information: This plan is only available to residential customers who sign up a new supply address, agree to direct debit, eCommunications and eBilling, meet our credit eligibility criteria and have the necessary metering system configuration.

gasContract.onExpiryDescription: The agreement continues until terminated by you or us in accordance with your terms and conditions.
